data.description: This home is a country dream with an amazing open view on the East side with close access to the Peavine trail. Fresh cut grass area on a .44 acre yard to relax with privacy. A detached garage for private storage with work table and cabinets. One story house with 3 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms with a hall office space, warm fireplace and a spare workroom on the enclosed front porch. New interior paint 2023, brand New roof 2022 and solar panels on garage to reduce utilities. Great location, easy to find, paved roads, close enough to town and also quiet with excellent neighbors! Excellent landscapes with mature trees, pear tree, peach trees, apple trees, strawberry garden box, continual growing herbs such as rosemary, basil and parsley. No smoking has been in the house. The friendly chickens stay in their coop and behind garage and give farm fresh eggs. Small shed for outdoor storage or clubhouse. Plenty of backyard for playground and trampoline. This house is a great place for family and friends, come check it out!
data.whatILove: Quiet peaceful yard. Open floor plan. Best neighborhood. Solar on detached garage. Chicken coop for your own farm fresh eggs.
